extensions.name: spotify-web
extensions.author: afkarxyz
extensions.description: Fetch Spotify metadata via web API. Supports personalized playlists like Daily Mix, Discover Weekly, and more. Includes Home Feed explore and full metadata enrichment (ISRC, label, copyright, genre) via SongLink/Deezer.

extensions.name: ytmusic-spotiflac
extensions.author: Amonoman and Zarz
extensions.description: YouTube Music Search Provider for SpotiFLAC. Search tracks, albums, and playlists on YouTube Music. Uses Odesli for ISRC lookup. Includes Home Feed explore.
